				<h3 id="post-7689"><a href="http://tradewithdave.com/?p=7689" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to 2:50 pm monday">2:50 pm monday</a></h3>
				<small>Monday, August 8th, 2011</small>

				<div class="entry">
					<div style="float: right; margin-left: 10px;"><a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-via="tradewithdave" data-count="vertical" data-url="http://tradewithdave.com/?p=7689">Tweet</a></div>
