<p class="facebook"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http://tradewithdave.com/?p=7689" target="_blank" title="Share on Facebook">Share on Facebook</a></p>				</div>

				<p class="postmetadata"> Posted in <a href="http://tradewithdave.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category">Uncategorized</a> |   <a href="http://tradewithdave.com/?p=7689#comments" title="Comment on 2:50 pm monday">3 Comments &#187;</a></p>

